MLflow 3.14 (what you're using)

Project/
│
├── mlflow.db          ← Backend Store
│
└── mlartifacts/       ← Artifact Store
    └── 2/
        ├── <run_id>/
        └── models/

mlflow.db stores:
    Experiments
    Runs
    Parameters
    Metrics
    Tags


mlartifacts/ stores:
    Models
    Images
    CSVs
    Plots
    Other logged files